      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. but a \"break\" just feels like more of the same. everything is just so... loud and tiring, and yet so empty. i find myself staring at the door and thinking how easy it would be to just not come back. to just let the silence take over completely. it almost feels peaceful to think about just disappearing for good, you know? like a way to finally stop trying to exist in a world that doesn't even see me.",
